  "response": "The best fishing bait depends on several factors, including:\n\n1. Type of fish you're targeting\n2. Location (freshwater or saltwater)\n3. Time of year\n4. Local conditions\n\nSome popular baits include:\n\nFreshwater:\n- Worms\n- Minnows\n- Crickets\n- Corn\n- PowerBait (for trout)\n- Nightcrawlers\n\nSaltwater:\n- Shrimp\n- Squid\n- Cut bait (pieces of fish)\n- Live bait like sardines or mullet\n\nArtificial lures are also effective for many species, such as:\n- Soft plastic worms\n- Crankbaits\n- Spinnerbaits\n- Jigs\n\nThe \"best\" bait varies, so it's recommended to ask local fishing shops or experienced anglers about specific recommendations for your area and target fish.",
